metadata.description: The action of The Alpha Lab takes place in two places, the outer world of real life struggles and romance and the inner retreat of meditation, the imaginary lab of the title. Along the way the hero, Matt, flirts with the panoply of New Age answers for the perennial answers posed by human beings. Matts frailty and halting progress reminds us all that getting where we want to be is not always plain sailing.
metadata.title: The Alpha Lab
metadata.subtitle: Novel For A New Age
metadata.name: The Alpha Lab
